Protocol
[[/cell]]
[[cell style="border: 1px solid black; padding: .3em .7em;"]]
Subject is presented with stew not containing peanuts and falsely informed that the stew contains peanuts. Subject compelled to eat stew.
[[/cell]]
[[/row]]
[[row]]
[[cell style="text-align: center; border: 1px solid black"]]
Results
[[/cell]]
[[cell style="border: 1px solid black; padding: .3em .7em;"]]
None.
