[[cell style="text-align: center; border: 1px solid black"]]
Protocol
[[/cell]]
[[cell style="border: 1px solid black; padding: .3em .7em;"]]
Protocol for previous test repeated. Before eating, subject is injected with a corticosteroid in order to induce a high level of stress.
[[/cell]]
[[/row]]
[[row]]
[[cell style="text-align: center; border: 1px solid black"]]
Results
[[/cell]]
[[cell style="border: 1px solid black; padding: .3em .7em;"]]
None.
