**Addendum 3:** An anonymous tip was submitted from a member of the on-site care ward staff concerning Researcher Richet's recent behavior, specifically his increased rate of testing, weakened rationale for testing procedure, and visible nervousness and irritability. A hearing was scheduled for 05/12/2025.

